\cf0  The National Museum of Singapore's Glass Rotunda has undergone a\
  revolutionary transformation into "Singapore Odyssea: A Journey Through\
  Time," setting new standards for heritage storytelling in the digital era.\
  This ambitious redevelopment project, spanning from April 2024 to August\
  2025, represents a bold vision to bridge Singapore's rich past with its\
  dynamic future through immersive technology and interactive experiences \'97\
  and the museum's signature gift to Singapore in celebration of the nation's\
  60th independence anniversary.\
\
  Launched on August 8, 2025, Singapore Odyssea is a 700-year immersive\
  journey through Singapore's rich history that seamlessly blends facts with\
  captivating myths, centering on the island nation's deep and enduring\
  relationship with the sea.\
